{"tid":2068692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇學佛巴打聽過 Little Buddha Bomjon","createTime":"2020-06-18T01:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T02:45:39.000Z","uid":54226,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85aa309c02859d870fce77e2c397919583c37093","tid":2068692,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEd7vcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEd7vcd.png&h=e2bed318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VSM1sYWKGJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVSM1sYWKGJY&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=55532f3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VSM1sYWKGJY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話佢喺樹下面冥想左幾十日 突然間會消失又突然間會出現。最後好似覺悟咗，而家傳緊佛法。<br />\n<br />\n但係有傳聞佢強姦同埋性侵佢嘅追隨者，而且佢有四個追隨者失咗蹤而家俾警察調查緊。所以想知各位學佛巴打點睇呢一個人，佢係唔係真係好似佛陀咁成咗佛，還是佢係外道？　　<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2019/01/10/asia/buddha-boy-ashram-intl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F01%2F10%2Fasia%2Fbuddha-boy-ashram-intl%2Findex.html&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=dda27318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F01%2F10%2Fasia%2Fbuddha-boy-ashram-intl%2Findex.html&h=ace4cfda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2019/01/10/asia/buddha-boy-ashram-intl/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"9bd6ca908fc7a0971a4ff4c8b546cb56ec0896b2","tid":2068692,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d2a86eb48e0faf90a4653a49a832050be54945d0","tid":2068692,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"召喚學佛巴"},{"pid":"d1699ef67caa81c65cc9cfe6b2a539e7f4a19405","tid":2068692,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T0